Currently, in the real estate, Bulgaria is undoubtedly the most popular target in Eastern Europe with its ski apartments and houses on the shores of the cheap sea.
In the mountains, the most popular areas are Bansko, Borovec, Pamprovo and Vitosa and, by the sea, Albena, the "Golden Sables", the "Sun Coast", the former Sozopol and Nessebar but they are increasingly searching for a building in the region of Kavarna and Balcik as well.
