In addition, many videos had already been broadcast on the net showing the areas of operations in Iraq and Afghanistan that were carried out on a real mission, but the British army had only been packed for the loading of these videos recently.
Americans are recruiting a little differently by using America's Army Downloadable Shooting Game for free. In this game the player can put himself directly to the soldiers as part of a more or less real simulation.
